  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Daman, Diu & DNH</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">The coastal areas (Daman and Diu) have a tropical maritime climate — warm year-round with distinct monsoon and winter seasons. October to March is ideal — pleasant temperatures (20–30°C), calm seas and clear skies. Dadra & Nagar Haveli's forest is most beautiful in October-November after the monsoon rains. Avoid June-September (heavy monsoon, rough seas) for beach tourism.</p>
